1. 基本语法
if x > 2
    puts "x > 2"
elsif x <= 2 and x != 0
    puts "x = 1"
else
    puts "unknown"
end

2. if修饰符
code if condition

3. unless
unless x > 2
    puts "x <= 2"
else
    puts "x > 2"
end

4. unless修饰符
code unless condition

5. case
$age =  5
case $age
when 0 .. 2
    puts "婴儿"
when 3 .. 6
    puts "小孩"
when 7 .. 12
    puts "child"
when 13 .. 18
    puts "少年"
else
    puts "其他年龄段的"
end
